title: 1982–83 Sheffield Wednesday F.C. season
text: During the 1982–83 season, the English <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club <a href="%3ASheffield%20Wednesday%20F.C.">:Sheffield Wednesday F.C.</a> was placed 6th in the <a href="%3AFootball%20League%20Second%20Division">:Football League Second Division</a>. The team reached the semifinal round of the <a href="%3AFA%20Cup">:FA Cup</a>.
